As we have said, we renew our commitment to our contractors and staff partners who work per hour.
All will be paid on the basis of their normal hours worked under normal circumstances.
This also applies if you are sick and cannot work.
If you want to work, you have our support.
Many people use work as a way to channel their stress with the world around us.
What we do can be incredibly rewarding, especially in these times.
Again, it is your personal care.
What we ask you to communicate with your manager so that we know what to expect and can adapt correctly.
